Dr. Oluwadare Kehinde (Hacco)Honourable Commissioner for Youth and Sports, Ogun State, has lauded Vice President Yemi Osinbajo as he clocks 64. ”I want to join millions of Nigerians especially the Youth Community worldwide to celebrate our highly revered, leader, mentor and Vice-President of the Federal Republic of Nigeria, Prof Yemi Osinbajo, GCON as he clocks Sixty Four (64) today Monday 8th March, 2021,” said in a press statement made available to NEWSVERGE. ”Those of us who have close encounters with Your Excellency can attest to your uncommon brilliance, rare humility and your penchant for Excellence. Your Excellency is a great leader, an inspirational icon, lover of the masses, and governance personified”,the Ogun youngest commissioner harped. ”With you at the forefront of political leadership in Nigeria, we are most certain that you will stop at nothing in creating the Nigeria of our dreams and restore our lost glories.” ”It is our prayer that you live long in health, wealth & peace of mind. We wish you many Happy Returns of the day Sir, and may you continue to advance in all dignity and honour.”